Somebody mentioned that the trial reset will fail in 10-20 mins and there is no fix yet. Actually there's a way to go about it but the process is quite tedious. For those who are already without licence may want to try this:

1) use trial reset to obtain new trial licence

within 10 minutes:

2) delete the new trial licence and remove kaspersky from your computer

3) re-install kaspersky, reboot and activate trial licence
